[code=java]		switch (npcs[i].npcType) {[/code]
add this
[code]	case 8528: //Nomad[/code]
Basically what this does is makes nomad aggressive so that he attacks people as soon as they get close enough to him.

next search for
[code=java]	public static int getAttackEmote(in[/code]
and under that switch statement add this
[code=java]case 8528: //Nomad
return 12696;[/code]
All this does is set nomad so he has his correct attack animation so he doesn't glitch.

then search for 
[code=java]public int getDeadEmote(int i) {[/code]
and in that switch statement add this.

[code=java]
case 8528: //Nomad
return 12694;[/code]
Basically same as previous, except this sets its death animation.

