Ok, Now to explain this.
Basically, All of the above code checks to see how much HP Nomad is on before doing a certain attack, For example if he has less than 5,000 lifepoints but more than 1,000, He will hit twice as quick and whereas, If he has less than 10,000 but more than 7,500 he will do blood barrage and heal himself 185 lifepoints per hit. This is easy enough to understand if you look at the code.

Finally in NPC.cfg add this
[code]npc	= 8528	Nomad	1001	30000[/code]

There you go, You now have a Nomad/Nex kind of system which you can expand, This is taken directly from my server which is on the status page, wont say name due to advertising.

